6a8dd52acf9164","tid":295790,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:40:32.000Z","msg":"當係電視咁用, 得唔得<br />\n想買部投影機+SOUND BAR代替電視, 有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9add60a6c5eab2194a69d7087e92333c3d06a1","tid":295790,"uid":13686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當係電視咁用, 得唔得<br />\n想買部投影機+SOUND BAR代替電視, 有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n低階唔用搵幕差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6b0b556a48e42317f0e5af7c7dbd6e59d07396","tid":295790,"uid":13686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當係電視咁用, 得唔得<br />\n想買部投影機+SOUND BAR代替電視, 有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n低階唔用拉幕差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"54337b341f158c433d121d9560aa4b2375a95441","tid":295790,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"我屋企投影機去屏幕2米半左右, 個screen 120吋緊緊投得晒, 已經set到最細, 如果無2米距離, 可能得60吋到80吋左右, 不如睇返電視算.<br />\n<br />\n用緊Epson tw5350"},{"pid":"9b2fbab4ca8634455839e178694ee1584413f3da","tid":295790,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你預幾錢畢直先<br />\n平既3 4百都有<br />\n貴既幾萬到<br />\n你要買映牆既一定要買流明高既<br />\n如果唔係d色淡到睇唔到<br />\n同買最好買led既<br />\n非led 白同黑都差好遠</blockquote><br />\n諗住平玩,1000樓下....唔知會唔會差到睇都冇隱...<br />\n諗住放係電腦台頂斜斜地射去牆"},{"pid":"4e47a293e77235d1fe7a0cc5bfa0221d50236918","tid":295790,"uid":73695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你預幾錢畢直先<br />\n平既3 4百都有<br />\n貴既幾萬到<br />\n你要買映牆既一定要買流明高既<br />\n如果唔係d色淡到睇唔到<br />\n同買最好買led既<br />\n非led 白同黑都差好遠</blockquote><br />\n諗住平玩,1000樓下....唔知會唔會差到睇都冇隱...<br />\n諗住放係電腦台頂斜斜地射去牆</blockquote><br />\n唔用幕顏色一定差<br />\n斜斜地畫面實變型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ffb40f21200a0597eaeb88a757fe9eb97ed24c","tid":295790,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你預幾錢畢直先<br />\n平既3 4百都有<br />\n貴既幾萬到<br />\n你要買映牆既一定要買流明高既<br />\n如果唔係d色淡到睇唔到<br />\n同買最好買led既<br />\n非led 白同黑都差好遠</blockquote><br />\n諗住平玩,1000樓下....唔知會唔會差到睇都冇隱...<br />\n諗住放係電腦台頂斜斜地射去牆</blockquote><br />\n唔用幕顏色一定差<br />\n斜斜地畫面實變型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梯形校正有冇用?<br />\n<br />\n如果冇辦法都要放棄"},{"pid":"a283b490d098ec8298437d6c910f3543f5805513","tid":295790,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:06:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6261173588a10f7c265afa5860abb0d2ee8beed","tid":295790,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote>"},{"pid":"613a80b825c1684d6c7ac9a2f831c975ebf77b68","tid":295790,"uid":70344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:35:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.y5.hk/product/lg-30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.y5.hk%2Fproduct%2Flg-30&d=JE8BUhBGfeezqiNcjQ6gaS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4bf3817c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.y5.hk/product/lg-30</a><br />\n<br />\n呢隻點睇"},{"pid":"c8676e4de841da3ebc085a8ca25541f28f5733c4","tid":295790,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"我以前都有玩開 有部benq 不過彩虹眼效應 所以放左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你最好去啲鋪頭睇下  望畫面會唔會有啲彩虹的散光係度 冇的就玩啦 有的就證明你隻眼唔適合玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d752d28f902206a4e49e585fe747f884655378","tid":295790,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201